                <div class="bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark rounded-3xl p-8 border border-gray-100 dark:border-slate-700 shadow-soft">
                    <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl mb-8 dark:text-white flex items-center gap-3">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" aria-hidden="true">school</span>
                        How to use Active Residents
                    </h2>
                    <div class="space-y-8 relative">
                        <div class="absolute left-[27px] top-8 bottom-8 w-0.5 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-slate-700" aria-hidden="true"></div>
                        <div class="flex gap-6 relative">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 rounded-full border-4 border-white dark:border-surface-dark flex items-center justify-center z-10">
                                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" aria-hidden="true">photo_camera</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="pt-1">
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold dark:text-white mb-2">1. Snap a Photo</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                                    Open the app and tap the large camera button. Take a clear photo of the issue (e.g., pothole, graffiti). Ensure the surrounding area is visible for context.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex gap-6 relative">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 rounded-full border-4 border-white dark:border-surface-dark flex items-center justify-center z-10">
                                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" aria-hidden="true">location_on</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="pt-1">
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold dark:text-white mb-2">2. Confirm Location</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                                    The app automatically detects your location using GPS. Verify the pin on the map is correct. You can drag the pin to adjust if necessary.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex gap-6 relative">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 rounded-full border-4 border-white dark:border-surface-dark flex items-center justify-center z-10">
                                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" aria-hidden="true">category</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="pt-1">
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold dark:text-white mb-2">3. Select Category</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                                    Choose the most appropriate category from the list (e.g., Road Maintenance, Waste, Lighting). This ensures your report reaches the right council department instantly.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex gap-6 relative">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20 rounded-full border-4 border-white dark:border-surface-dark flex items-center justify-center z-10">
                                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-green-500" aria-hidden="true">check_circle</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="pt-1">
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold dark:text-white mb-2">4. Submit &amp; Track</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                                    Hit submit! You'll receive a notification when the council views your report and another when the issue has been resolved.
                                </p>
                            </div>
