                        </summary>
                        <div class="px-6 pb-6 pt-0">
                            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
                                You can change your default council area in the Settings menu. Go to Profile &gt; Settings &gt; Location Preferences. Note that you can report issues in any council area regardless of your home setting; the app detects your current location automatically.
                            </p>
