                            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">The app says "Location not found". What do I do?</h3>
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-gray-400 group-open:text-primary group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-300" aria-hidden="true">expand_more</span>
                        </summary>
                        <div class="px-6 pb-6 pt-0">
                            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
                                Please ensure that Location Services are enabled for Active Residents in your phone's settings.
                                <br/><br/>
                                <strong>iOS:</strong> Settings &gt; Privacy &gt; Location Services &gt; Active Residents &gt; While Using the App.<br/>
                                <strong>Android:</strong> Settings &gt; Location &gt; App permissions &gt; Active Residents &gt; Allow only while using the app.
