                        <div>
                            <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl mb-4">Still need help?</h2>
                            <p class="text-blue-100 mb-6 max-w-md">
                                Can't find what you're looking for? Our dedicated support team is here to assist you with any technical issues or inquiries.
                            </p>
                            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
                                <a class="bg-white text-blue-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors flex items-center justify-center gap-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-white" href="mailto:support@activeresidents.co.uk">
                                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined" aria-hidden="true">mail</span>
                                    Email Support
                                </a>
                                <a class="bg-blue-700 border border-blue-500 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-blue-600 transition-colors flex items-center justify-center gap-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-white" href="#">
                                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined" aria-hidden="true">chat</span>
                                    Live Chat
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="hidden md:block">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-9xl text-white/20" aria-hidden="true">support_agent</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
    </div>

    <footer class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 pt-20 pb-10 border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-slate-800">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-16">
                <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-2">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
                        <img src="secondary logo.png" alt="Active Residents Icon" class="h-20 w-auto">
                        <span class="font-display font-bold text-xl dark:text-white">Active<span class="text-primary">Residents</span></span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-text-sub-light dark:text-text-sub-dark max-w-sm">Empowering communities through technology. Building better neighborhoods, one report at a time.</p>
                    <p class="text-text-sub-light dark:text-text-sub-dark text-sm mt-4">
                        <a href="mailto:noreply@activeresidents.co.uk" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">noreply@activeresidents.co.uk</a>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold mb-6 dark:text-white">Product</h4>
                    <ul class="space-y-4 text-text-sub-light dark:text-text-sub-dark text-sm">
                        <li><a class="hover:text-primary transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary rounded" href="#">Features</a></li>
                    </ul>
